---
// Footer.astro
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-surface-dim border-t border-white/5 pt-16 pb-8 mt-24 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none -z-10 translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-[80px] pointer-events-none -z-10 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16">
      
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6 group">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary to-blue-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 group-hover:shadow-primary/40 transition-all border border-white/10">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">WaForge</span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-text-muted max-w-sm text-base leading-relaxed">
          La piattaforma CRM completa per scalare l'assistenza e le vendite tramite WhatsApp, progettata per le agenzie.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-6 tracking-wide text-sm uppercase">Prodotto</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li><a href="/#features" class="text-text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm">Funzionalità</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#pricing" class="text-text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm">Prezzi</a></li>
          <li><a href="/integrazioni" class="text-text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm">Integrazioni</a></li>
          <li><a href="/changelog" class="text-text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm">Changelog</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-6 tracking-wide text-sm uppercase">Azienda</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li><a href="/about" class="text-text-muted hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm">Chi Siamo</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contatti" class="text-text-muted hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm">Contatti</a></li>
          <li><a href="/privacy" class="text-text-muted hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm">Privacy Policy</a></li>
          <li><a href="/terms" class="text-text-muted hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm">Termini di Servizio</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
    </div>
    
    <div class="pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm text-center md:text-left">
        &copy; {year} WaForge Inc. Tutti i diritti riservati.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <!-- Social Icons -->
        <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-text-muted hover:text-primary hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"></path></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-text-muted hover:text-primary hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M23 3a10.9 10.9 0 0 1-3.14 1.53 4.48 4.48 0 0 0-7.86 3v1A10.66 10.66 0 0 1 3 4s-4 9 5 13a11.64 11.64 0 0 1-7 2c9 5 20 0 20-11.5a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-.08-.83A7.72 7.72 0 0 0 23 3z"></path></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
